<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>로그인 페이지</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" media="screen" href="/css/login.css">
</head>
<body>
<div class="container">
    <div class="logo">
        <img src="./img/로고.png" alt="로고">
    </div>
    <div class="login-form">
        <p class="login-info">로그인이 필요한 서비스입니다. <br> 아이디와 비밀번호를 입력하여 접속해주세요.</p>
        <br>
        <form id="loginForm">
            <div class="input-group">
                <label for="username">아이디</label>
                <input type="text" id="userid" name="userid" placeholder="아이디를 입력하세요" required>
            </div>
            <div class="input-group">
                <label for="password">비밀번호</label>
                <input type="password" id="userpwd" name="userpwd" placeholder="비밀번호를 입력하세요" required>
            </div>
            <button type="submit">로그인</button>
        </form>
        <p><a href="./아이디 찾기.html">아이디 찾기</a> | <a href="./비밀번호 찾기.html">비밀번호 찾기</a></p>
        <p>아직 회원이 아니신가요? <a href="./회원가입.html">회원가입</a></p>
    </div>
</div>

<script src="/js/login.js"></script>
</body>
</html>